                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="flashcard-container" id="leaf-card-4" style="display:none;">
                            <div class="flashcard" onclick="flipCard('leaf-card-4')" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-label="Flashcard: Bipinnate leaf" onkeypress="if(event.key==='Enter') flipCard('leaf-card-4')">
                                <div class="flashcard-front">
                                    <h3>Bipinnate</h3>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flashcard-back">
                                    <p>Twice-divided pinnate leaves. Example: <em>Acacia dealbata</em> (Silver Wattle) has bipinnate leaves.</p>
                                </div>
