Step 2: Add ARIA Live Regions to Your Body

Add these lines right after your <body> tag (around line 240):

```html
<body>
    <!-- ARIA Live Region for Screen Reader Announcements -->
    <div aria-live="polite" id="aria-live-region" class="sr-only"></div>
    <div aria-live="assertive" id="aria-assertive-region" class="sr-only"></div>
    
    <!-- Skip to main content link for accessibility -->
    <a href="#main-content" class="sr-only focus-visible" style="position: absolute; top: 10px; left: 10px; background: white; padding: 0.5rem; z-index: 1000;">Skip to main content</a>
    
    <!-- Your existing header -->
    <header>
        ...
    </header>
```

